Point Grey FireFly MV INDI driver
=================================
This package provides the INDI driver for the Point Grey FireFly MV camera.

Requirements
============
* INDI
* CFITSIO
* LIBDC1394


Installation
============
See INSTALL


How to Use
==========
Once installed, the FireFly MV INDI driver can be used by an INDI client such as
KStars (Ekos) or OpenPHD. It can also be used manually by invoking it via the 
indi_server:
$ indi_server indi_ffmv_ccd


